list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Update valuation-dlg stub
Implemented validation methods for different input related controls in the dialog used for a new measurement range adding. A distinction still needs to be made for handling the invalid text field/area red border. Some different warning popups are also needed to indicate the control holding the invalid input.

task.summary:
Update valuation sub-tab
Implemented the functionality that adds/removes extra AC frequency levels to the existing VAC and IAC sections. Up to 10 additional frequencies may be added to each of those functions.

Add valuation-dlg stub
Implemented an initial version of this dialog for adding new measurement range / points to a desired TableView. Fixed some issues with the data transfer between the dialog controller and the ValuationController.
